{"title":"红柳","authors":["李幼容"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":3,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李幼容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报社记者下农场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要给支边姑娘拍张像。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘引着记者到场外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳丛中笑脸仰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“当年我们来边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就从这里建新场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风餐露宿沙包上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳相依情谊长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红柳干，架房梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳根，煮饭汤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折枝红柳做筷子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嚼不尽创业生活多甜香！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红柳条，编成防风障，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来今日绿树千里护农场；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳叶，沤绿肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换来稻花万顷浪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红柳是我们的好伙伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一同扎根在边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风沙高一尺，身材长三丈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的花象战旗迎风扬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“明晨出征建新场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳丛留张纪念像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记者同志请您看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个镜头可理想？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记者点头忙对光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘笑立红柳旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照相机快门喀嚓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摄下了塔里木的青春形象！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}